EmailTemplate.subject: DR Summer Internship - Orientation Information
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hello Live Different Build Summer Interns!
Please read over and respond so I know you have read and acknowledged this email!
INTERN ORIENTATION SCHEDULE
A schedule is attached to this e-mail, please read it over to see what we will be doing on the first day.
VOLUNTEER ORIENTATION MANUAL
A manual is attached to this e-mail, please read it over thoroughly, as this is important for interns to know before arriving.
PRESENTATION OF INTERN ASSIGNMENTS
Out of your 1st, 2nd and 3rd assignment, I would like you to choose your best assignment to present to your fellow interns on Orientation Day, You will have a maximum of 10 minutes to show your project and to explain and elaborate a little more about it. Once you have decide, please e-mail me back so I can have this prepared on Orientation Day.
ASSIGNMENT #4
This assignment is due tomorrow!
Please feel free to email me with any of your questions,
See you in two weeks!
